{"word":"H3847 - לָבַשׁ - lâbash - law-bash' - Apparel","slug":"H3847","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">לָבַשׁ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>lâbash"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>law-bash'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Apparel"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DC;&#x05D1;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DC;&#x05D1;&#x05E9;&#x05C1; - la&#x0302;bash  la&#x0302;be&#x0302;sh</b> - <i>law-bash', law-bashe'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly <i>wrap</i> around, that is, (by implication) to <i>put on</i> a garment or <i>clothe</i> (oneself, or another), literally or figuratively: - (in) apparel, arm, array (self), clothe (self), come upon, put (on, upon), wear."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1688\">H1688</a>, <a href=\"#/H3830\">H3830</a>, <a href=\"#/H3849\">H3849</a>, <a href=\"#/H3850\">H3850</a>, <a href=\"#/H4403\">H4403</a>, <a href=\"#/H8516\">H8516</a>"}]}